---
title: Beef & Beetroot Relish Burger with Potato Wedges & Herby Mayo
description: Say goodbye to takeaway when you whip up these mouth-watering burgers. Paired with homemade beetroot relish and a herby
mayo that amplifies the rich flavour of the succulent beef patties, these are sure to be a guaranteed hit!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/herby-lamb-burger-d16fcbd0.jpg
